(280, 1, '2019-02-06 14:16:53', '2019-02-06 11:16:53', '<strong>New constructions</strong>\r\nControlled air renewal throughout the year through an air renewal system or automated windows for all building categories, except the Industry and Warehouse categories, is mandatory. In the MINERGIE® justificatory, specifications for the quantification of the expenditure of \"small\" ventilation systems (less than 1000 m3/h) are presented.\r\nFor the calculation of the energy expenditure of the larger ventilation systems, the ventilation-cooling tool according to SIA 380/4 is available. This tool will eventually replace the excel spreadsheet excerpt tables used so far. For now, both tools can be used for MINERGIE® justificatory.', 'Rotary recuperator (very good efficiency/very high yield). Type 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rotary-recuperator-very-good-efficiency-very-high-yield-type-1', '', '', '2019-03-06 19:37:16', '2019-03-06 16:37:16', '', 0, 'http://broodd.zzz.com.ua/?post_type=offer&#038;p=280', 27, 'offer', '', 0);
