(350, 1, '2019-02-28 11:27:17', '2019-02-28 08:27:17', '<strong>Description</strong>\n• System for gentle ventilation of individual rooms.\n• Implementation in peripheral rooms of buildings with a conventional ventilation system for several rooms.\n• Posterior installation in old buildings without simultaneous renovation.\n• Multi-storey operation.\n• Can not be combined with air-to-ground register or heat pump on extract air.\n• Reduced efficiency of heat recovery.\n\n<strong>Requirements</strong>\n• All living and working rooms and bedrooms of the building as well as toilet blocks must be ventilated mechanically.\n\n<strong>Recommendation</strong>\n• In bedrooms, appliances must meet the increased requirements of SIA 181 for standard sound level difference (DnT, w).', 'Double-flow gentle ventilation for individual room. Type 2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '294-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-02-28 11:27:17', '2019-02-28 08:27:17', '', 294, 'http://broodd.zzz.com.ua/294-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
